Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.38,0:02:05.65,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}我所不足的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:09.29,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}君が全部持ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:09.29,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}你却全部拥有
